attributes.value: / > SBI functions must return a pair of values in a0 and a1,
/ > with a0 returning an error code.
/ > This is analogous to returning the C structure `SbiRet`.

defs.name: Error
defs.value:
pub enum Error {
    Failed,
    NotSupported,
    InvalidParam,
    Denied,
    InvalidAddress,
    AlreadyAvailable,
    AlreadyStarted,
    AlreadyStopped,
    Customed(isize),
}

defs.name: into_result
defs.value: pub const fn into_result(Self) -> Result<usize, Error>
